race.comment: SHOW ME THE STARS (14) was a long way back last start but hit the line well to finish fifth, beaten 1.5 lengths, over 1400m at Sunshine Coast. Can easily finish right over the top of these. CHANCE WITH WOLVES (12) continued the encouraging form and wasn't far away last time when second over 1650m at Doomben. Has a good gate and gets his chance to break through. GO MARO (8) finished 12th last start at Eagle Farm over 1600m in a disappointing performance. Look for an improved run here. NOTACLUEHOWORWHO (11) was below his best when resuming last start, beaten 4.5 lengths into sixth over 1400m at Dalby. Makes plenty of appeal second up.
